textBeforeTable: User name is string. user(string) The specified tag by name, or all tagged revisions if no name is given. tag(name) Changesets with no parent changeset in set. roots(set) Revision with the given numeric identifier. rev(number) An empty set, if any revision in set isn't found; otherwise, all revisions in set. present(set) The set of all parents for all changesets in set, or the working directory. parents([set]) Second parent of changesets in set, or the working directory. p2([set]) First parent of changesets in set, or the working directory. p1([set]) Changeset with lowest revision number in set. min(set) Changeset is a merge changeset. merge() Changeset with highest revision number in set. max(set) First n members of set. limit(set, n) Search commit message, user name, and names of changed files for string. keyword(string) Revision non-ambiguously specified by the given hex string prefix. id(string) Members of set with no children in set. heads(set) Changeset is a named branch head. head() grep(r'...')
